quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  27,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  27,1,Taa-Seeen- . yeh quran aur roshan kitaab ki ayatain hain
  27,2,mominoun ke liye hadaayat aur basharat
  27,3,woh jo namaz parhte aur zakaat dete aur akhirat ka yaqeen rakhtay hain
  27,4,jo log akhirat par imaan nahi rakhtay hain hum ne un ke aamaal un ke liye آرستہ kardiye hain to woh srgrdan ho rahay hain
  27,5,yahi log hain jin ke liye bara azaab hai aur woh akhirat mein bhi woh bohat nuqsaan uthany walay hain
  27,6,aur tum ko quran ( khuday-e ) hakeem o aleem ki taraf se ataakiya jata hai
  27,7,"jab moose ne apne ghar walon se kaha ke mein ne aag dekhi hai, mein wahan se ( raste ) ka pata lata hon ya sulagta howa angara tumahray paas lata hon taakay tum tappo"
  27,8,jab moose is ke paas aeye to nida aayi ke woh jo aag mein ( tajallii dekhata ) hai babarkat hai. aur jo aag ke ird gird hain aur khuda jo tamam aalam ka perwar-digaar hai pak hai
  27,9,ae moose mein hi khuday-e ghalib ودانا hon
  27,10,aur apni laathi daal do. jab ussay dekha to ( is terhan ) hil rahi thi goya saanp hai to peeth phair kar bhage aur peechay murr kar nah dekha ( hukum howa ke ) moose daro mat. hamaray paas paighambar dara nahi karte
  27,11,haan jis ne zulmkiya phir buraiee ke baad usay neki se badal diya to mein bakhsnay wala meharban hon
  27,12,aur apna haath apne garibaan mein daalo safaid niklay ga. ( un do majzon ke sath jo ) no majzon mein ( daakhil hain ) firaon aur is ki qoum ke paas jao ke woh be hukum log hain
  27,13,"jab un ke paas hamari roshan nishanain pohnchain, kehnay lagey yeh Sarih jaadoo hai"
  27,14,aur be insafi aur ghuroor se un se inkaarkiya lekin un ke dil un ko maan chuke they. so dekh lau fasaad karne walon ka injaam kaisa howa
  27,15,aur hum ne dawod aur Sulaiman ko ilm bakhsha aur unhon ne kaha ke khuda ka shukar hai jis ne hamein bohat se momin bundon par fazliat di
  27,16,aur Sulaiman aur dawod ke qaim maqam hue. aur kehnay lagey ke logo! hamein ( khuda ki taraf se ) janwaron ki boli sikhayi gayi hai aur har cheez inayat farmai gayi hai. be shak yeh ( uss ka ) Sarih fazl hai
  27,17,aur Sulaiman ke liye junoo aur insanon aur parindon ke lashkar jama kiye gay aur qisam waar kiye jatay they
  27,18,yahan taq ke jab chyontyon ke maidan mein puhanche to aik choonti ne kaha ke chyontyon apne apne bilon mein daakhil ho jao aisa nah ho ke Sulaiman aur is ke lashkar tum ko kuchal dalain aur un ko khabar bhi nah ho
  27,19,to woh is ki baat sun kar hans parre aur kehnay lagey ke ae perwar-digaar! mujhe tofeq ataa farma ke jo ahsaan tunay mujh par aur mere maa baap par kiye hain un ka shukar karoon aur aisay naik kaam karoon ke to un se khush hojaye aur mujhe apni rehmat se apne naik bundon mein daakhil farma
  27,20,unhon ne janwaron ka jaiza liya to kehnay lageykiya sabab hai ke hudhud nazar nahi aata.kiya kahin gayab hogaya hai ?
  27,21,mein usay sakht saza dun ga ya zibah kar daloon ga ya mere samnay ( apni be Qasuri ki ) Daleel Sarih paish kere
  27,22,abhi thori hi der hui thi ke hudhud aa mojood howa aur kehnay laga ke mujhe aik aisi cheez maloom hui hai jis ki aap ko khabar nahi aur mein aap ke paas ( shehar ) Saba se aik sachhi khabar le kar aaya hon
  27,23,mein ne aik aurat dekhi ke un logon par badshahat karti hai aur har cheez usay muyassar hai aur is ka aik bara takhat hai
  27,24,mein ne dekha ke woh aur is ki qoum khuda ko chore kar aftaab ko sajda karte hain aur shetan ne un ke aamaal inhen aaraasta kar dukhaay hain aur un ko raste se rok rakha hai pas woh raste par nahi aeye
  27,25,( aur nahi samajte ) ke khuda ko asmano aur zameen mein chhupi cheezon ko zahir kardaita aur tumahray posheeda aur zahir aamaal ko jaanta hai kyun sajda nah karen
  27,26,khuda ke siwa koi ibadat ke Laiq nahi wohi arsh azeem ka maalik hai
  27,27,"Sulaiman ne kaha ( acha ) hum dekhen ge, tunay sach kaha hai ya to jhoota hai"
  27,28,yeh mera khat le ja aur usay un ki taraf daal day phir un ke paas se phir aa aur dekh ke wohkiya jawab dete hain
  27,29,malka ne kaha ke darbaar walo! meri taraf aik nama graami dala gaya hai
  27,30,woh Sulaiman ki taraf se hai aur mazmoon yeh hai ke shuru khuda ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  27,31,( baad is ke yeh ) ke mujhe sar kashi nah karo aur Mutee ومنقاد ho kar mere paas chalay aao
  27,32,"( khat suna kar ) woh kehnay lagi ke ae ahal darbaar mere is muamlay mein mujhe mahswara do, jab taq tum haazir nah ho ( aur Salah nah do ) mein kisi kaam ko Faisal karne wali nahi"
  27,33,woh bolay ke hum barray zorawar aur sakht jangju hain aur hukum aap ke ikhtiyar hai to jo hukum dijiye ga ( is ke maal par ) nazar kar liji-ay ga
  27,34,is ne kaha ke badshah jab kisi shehar mein daakhil hotay hain to is ko tabah kar dete hain aur wahan ke izzat walon ko zaleel kar diya karte hain aur isi terhan yeh bhi karen ge
  27,35,aur mein un ki taraf kuch tohfa bhijti hon aur dekhatii hon ke qasidkiya jawab laatay hain
  27,36,"jab ( qasid ) Sulaiman ke paas pouncha to Sulaiman ne kahakiya tum mujhe maal se madad dena chahtay ho, jo kuch khuda ne mujhe ataa farmaya hai woh is se behtar hai jo tumhe diya hai haqeeqat yeh hai ke tum hi apne tohfay se khush hotay hogay"
  27,37,un ke paas wapas jao hum un par aisay lashkar se hamla karen ge jis ke muqablay ki un mein taaqat nah hogi aur un ko wahan se be izzat karkay nikaal den ge aur woh zaleel hon ge
  27,38,Sulaiman ne kaha ke ae darbaar walo! koi tum mein aisa hai ke qabal is ke ke woh log farmanbardar ho kar hamaray paas ayen malka ka takhat mere paas le aeye
  27,39,jaanat mein se aik quwwat hekal jin ne kaha ke qabal is ke ke aap apni jagah se utheen mein is ko aap ke paas la hazir karta hon aur mein is ( ke uthany ki ) taaqat rakhta hon ( aur ) amanat daar hon
  27,40,1 shakhs jis ko kitaab Ellahi ka ilm tha kehnay laga ke mein aap ki aankhh ke jhapkane se pehlay pehlay usay aap ke paas haazir kiye deta hon. jab Sulaiman ne takhat ko apne paas rakha howa dekha to kaha ke yeh mere perwar-digaar ka fazl hai taakay mujhe aazamaa_e ke mein shukar karta hon ya kufran Nemat karta hon aur jo shukar karta hai to apne hi faiday ke liye shukar karta hai aur jo nashukri karta hai to mera perwar-digaar be parwa ( aur ) karam karne wala hai
  27,41,Sulaiman ne kaha ke malka ke ( imthehaan aqal ke ) liye is ke takhat ki soorat badal do. dekhen ke woh soojh rakhti hai ya un logon mein hai jo soojh nahi rakhtay
  27,42,jab woh aa pohanchi to poocha gaya kekiya aap ka takhat bhi isi terhan ka hai? is ne kaha ke yeh to goya ho baho wohi hai aur hum ko is se pehlay hi ( Sulaiman ki Azmat shaan ) ka ilm hogaya tha aur hum farmanbardar hain
  27,43,"aur woh jo khuda ke siwa ( aur ki ) parastish karti thi, Sulaiman ne is ko is se manakiya ( is se pehlay to ) woh kafiroon mein se thi"
  27,44,"( phir ) is se kaha gaya ke mehal mein chaliye, jab is ne is ( ke farsh ) ko dekha to usay pani ka hoz samgha aur ( kapra utha kar ) apni pindliyan khol den. Sulaiman ne kaha yeh aisa mehal hai jis mein ( neechay bhi ) sheeshay jurey hue hain. woh bol uthi ke perwar-digaar mein apne aap par zulm karti rahi thi aur ( ab ) mein Sulaiman ke haath par khuday-e rab alaalmin par imaan latayen hon"
  27,45,aur hum ne smod ki taraf is ke bhai Saleh ko bheja ke khuda ki ibadat karo to woh do fareeq ho kar aapas mein jhagrnay lagey
  27,46,Saleh ne kaha ke bhayyo tum bhalai se pehlay buraiee ke liye kyun jaldi karte ho ( aur ) khuda se bakhshish kyun nahi mangte taakay tum par rehamkiya jaye
  27,47,woh kehnay lagey ke tum aur tumahray saathi hamaray liye shagoon bad hai. Saleh ne kaha ke tumhari bdshgoni khuda ki taraf se hai balkay tum aisay log ho jin ki azmaish ki jati hai
  27,48,aur shehar mein no shakhs they jo malik mein fasaadkiya karte they aur islaah se kaam nahi letay they
  27,49,kehnay lagey ke khuda ki qasam khao ke hum raat ko is par aur is ke ghar walon par shab khoon marain ge phir is ke waris se keh den ge ke hum to Saleh ke ghar walon ke mauqa halakat par gay hi nahi aur hum sach kehte hain
  27,50,aur woh aik chaal chalay aur un ko kuch khabar nah hui
  27,51,to dekh lau un ki chaal ka kaisa injaam howa. hum ne un ko aur un ki qoum sab ko halaak kar dala
  27,52,"ab yeh un ke ghar un ke zulm ke sabab khaali parre hain. jo log Danish rakhtay hain, un ke liye is mein nishani hai"
  27,53,aur jo log imaan laaye aur drtay they un ko hum ne nijaat di
  27,54,aur Loot ko ( yaad karo ) jab unhon ne apni qoum se kaha ke tum be hiyai ( ke kaam ) kyun karte ho aur tum dekhte ho
  27,55,kiya tum aurton ko chore kar ( lazzat haasil karne ) ke liye mardon ki taraf mael hotay ho. haqeeqat yeh hai ke tum ahmaq log ho
  27,56,to un ki qoum ke log ( bolay to ) yeh bolay aur is ke siwa un ka kuch jawab nah tha ke Loot ke ghar walon ko apne shehar se nikaal do. yeh log pak rehna chahtay hain
  27,57,to hum ne un ko aur un ke ghar walon ko nijaat di. magar un ki biwi ke is ki nisbat hum ne muqarrar kar rakha hai ( ke woh peechay rehne walon mein hogi )
  27,58,"aur hum ne un parmeinhہ barsaya so ( jo )meinhہ un logon par barsa jin ko mutnabba kardiya gaya tha, bura tha"
  27,59,keh do ke sab tareef khuda hi ko sazawar hai aur is ke bundon par salam hai jin ko is ne munhtakhib farmaya. bhala khuda behtar hai ya woh jin ko yeh ( is ka shareek ) th_hrate hain
  27,60,bhala kis ne asmano aur zameen ko pedakiya aur ( kis ne ) tumahray liye aasman se pani barsaya. ( hum ne ) phir hum hi ne is se sirsabz baagh ugaye. tumhara kaam to nah tha ke tum unn ke darakhton ko agate. tokiya khuda ke sath koi aur bhi mabood hai? ( hargiz nahi ) balkay yeh log raste se allag ho rahay hain
  27,61,bhala kis ne zameen ko qarar gaah banaya aur is ke beech nehrain banayen aur is ke liye pahar banaye aur ( kis ne ) do daryaaon ke beech oot banai ( yeh sab kuch khuda ne banaya ) tokiya khuda ke sath koi aur mabood bhi hai? ( hargiz nahi ) balkay un mein aksar Danish nahi rakhtay
  27,62,bhala kon bekraar ki iltija qubool karta hai. jab woh is se dua karta hai aur ( kon is ki ) takleef ko daur karta hai aur ( kon ) tum ko zameen mein ( uglo ka ) janasheen banata hai ( yeh sab kuch khuda karta hai ) tokiya khuda ke sath koi aur mabood bhi hai ( hargiz nahi magar ) tum bohat kam ghhor karte ho
  27,63,bhala kon tum ko jungle aur darya ke andheron mein rasta banata hai aur ( kon ) hawaon ko apni rehmat ke agay khushkhabri banakar bhejta hai ( yeh sab kuch khuda karta hai ) tokiya khuda ke sath koi aur mabood bhi hai? ( hargiz nahi ). yeh log jo shirk karte hain khuda ( ki shaan ) is se buland hai
  27,64,bhala kon khalqat ko pehli baar peda karta. phir is ko baar baar peda karta rehta hai aur ( kon ) tum ko aasman aur zameen se rizaq deta hai ( yeh sab kuch khuda karta hai ) tokiya khuda ke sath koi aur mabood bhi hai ( hargiz nahi ) keh do ke ( mushrako ) agar tum sachey ho to Daleel paish karo
  27,65,keh do ke jo log asmano aur zameen mein hain khuda ke siwa ghaib ki baatein nahi jantay. aur nah yeh jantay hain ke kab ( zindah karkay ) uthaye jayen ge
  27,66,balkay akhirat ( ke baray ) mein un ka ilm munhtahi hochuka hai balkay woh is se shak mein hain. balkay is se andhay ho rahay hain
  27,67,aur jo log kafir hain kehte hain jab hum aur hamaray baap dada matti ho jayen ge tokiya hum phir ( qabron se ) nikalay jayen ge
  27,68,yeh wada hum se aur hamaray baap dada se pehlay se hota chala aaya hai ( kahan ka uthna aur kaisi qayamat ) yeh to sirf pehlay logon ki kahaniyan hain
  27,69,keh do ke malik mein chalo phiro phir dekho ke gunahgaaron ka injaamkiya howa hai
  27,70,aur un ( ke haal ) par gham nah karna aur nah unn chalon se jo yeh kar rahay hain tang dil hona
  27,71,aur kehte hain ke agar tum sachey ho to yeh wada kab poora hoga ?
  27,72,keh do ke jis ( azaab ) ke liye tum jaldi kar rahay ho shayad is mein se kuch tumahray nazdeek aap_hncha ho
  27,73,aur tumhara perwar-digaar to logon par fazl karne wala hai lekin un mein se aksar shukar nahi karte
  27,74,aur jo baatein un ke seenon mein posheeda hoti hain aur jo kaam woh zahir karte hain tumhara perwar-digaar un ( sab ) ko jaanta hai
  27,75,aur asmano aur zameen mein koi posheeda cheez nahi hai magar ( woh ) kitaab roshan mein ( likhi hui ) hai
  27,76,"be shak yeh quran bani Israel ke samnay aksar baatein jin mein woh ikhtilaaf karte hain, bayan kar deta hai"
  27,77,aur be shak yeh mominoun ke liye Hadayat aur rehmat hai
  27,78,tumhara perwar-digaar ( qayamat ke roz ) unn mein apne hukum se faisla kar day ga aur woh ghalib ( aur ) ilm wala hai
  27,79,to khuda par bharosa rakho tum to haq Sarih par ho
  27,80,kuch shak nahi ke tum mardon ko ( baat ) nahi suna satke aur nah behroon ko jab ke woh peeth phair kar phir jayen aawaz suna satke ho
  27,81,aur nah andhon ko gumraahi se ( nikaal kar ) rasta dekha satke ho. tum un hi ko suna satke ho jo hamari aayton par imaan laatay hain aur woh farmanbardar ho jatay hain
  27,82,aur jab unn ke baray mein ( azaab ) ka wada poora hoga to hum unn ke liye zameen mein se aik janwar nikalen ge jo un se bayan kar day ga. is liye ke log hamari aayton par imaan nahi laatay they
  27,83,aur jis roz hum har aُmt mein se is giroh ko jama karen ge jo hamari aayton ki takzieeb karte they to unn ki jamaat bandi ki jaye gi
  27,84,yahan taq ke jab ( sab ) ajayeen ge to ( khuda ) farmaiye ga kekiya tum ne meri aayton ko jhutla diya tha aur tum ne ( apne ) ilm se un par ihata tokiya hi nah tha. bhala tumkiya karte they
  27,85,aur unn ke zulm ke sabab unn ke haq mein wada ( azaab ) poora hokar rahay ga to woh bol bhi nah saken ge
  27,86,kiya onhon ne nahi dekha ke hum ne raat ko ( is liye ) banaya hai ke is mein aaraam karen aur din ko roshan ( banaya hai ke is mein kaam karen ) be shak is mein momin logon ke liye nishanain hain
  27,87,aur jis roz sor phonka jaye ga to jo log asmano aur zameen mein hain sab ghabra uthen ge magar woh jisay khuda chahay aur sab is ke paas aajiz ho kar chalay ayen ge
  27,88,aur tum pahoron ko dekhte ho to khayaal karte ho ke ( apni jagah par ) kharray hain magar woh ( is roz ) is terhan uday phrin ge jaisay baadal. ( yeh ) khuda ki karigari hai jis ne har cheez ko mazboot banaya. be shak woh tumahray sab af-aal se bakhabar hai
  27,89,jo shakhs neki le kar aeye ga to is ke liye is se behtar ( badla tayyar ) hai aur aisay log ( uss roz ) ghabrahat se be khauf hon ge
  27,90,aur jo buraiee le kar aeye ga to aisay log avndhe munh dozakh mein daal diye jayen ge. tum ko to unn hi aamaal ka badla miley ga jo tum karte rahay ho
  27,91,( keh do ) ke mujh ko yahi irshad howa hai ke is shehar ( mecca ) ke maalik ki ibadat karoon jis ne is ko mohtaram ( aur maqam adab ) banaya hai aur sab cheez usi ki hai aur yeh bhi hukum howa hai ke is ka hukum bardaar rahon
  27,92,aur yeh bhi ke quran parha karoon. to jo shakhs raah raast ikhtiyar karta hai to apne hi faiday ke liye ikhtiyar karta hai. aur jo gumraah rehta hai to keh do ke mein to sirf nasiyaat karne wala hon
  27,93,aur kaho ke khuda ka shukar hai. woh tum ko anqareeb apni nishanain dukhaay ga to tum unn ko pehchan lau ge. aur jo kaam tum karte ho tumhara perwar-digaar unn se be khabar nahi hai
